            <h1>How to Tie a Scarf - Men&rsquo;s Scarves</h1>
            <p>How do you tie together a sharp fall/winter look? Besides keeping your neck warm, a men&rsquo;s scarf is a stylish topper for your jackets and coats this cold-weather season. From popping prints to standard solids, scope out the perfect <a href="{{ENV_HOSTNAME}}/shop/b/mens-scarves?id=73159">men&rsquo;s scarves</a> to complete your look at Macy&rsquo;s.</p>
        </div>
